Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:02:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為組成人的 也可能是時間麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷漫長的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積累了經驗 經歷了諸多相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是這麼形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那的確不是全部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:02:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二話 為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山色青麗 晨事皆畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有賴床 萬事如意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣搞定 就怕下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然襲擊 那就完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親說了 不會下的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係 沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文…人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首很可愛的歌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「父親說了 不會下的 沒有關係」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呀 連歌裡都出現你爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為父親說天晴 就一定會晴好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為唯芳先生看過天氣預報了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是父親說的準沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜真的很喜歡爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:05:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給小夜的獎勵 大清早就勤勞地洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從洗衣那裡就聽到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聲音有那麼大麼 唱歌的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很有朝氣的歌聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 叫做「Guimauve」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和這個店的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜一直都要黑咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 因為很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有一天沒喝這裡的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得自己靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我覺得和咖啡很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是很奇妙的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能喜歡真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前父親給的麩饅頭也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs45}麩饅頭：一種日式茶點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只要是甜的我都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看唯芳先生那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜歡甜食呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是 他都不太和我一起吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我吃東西時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會做出什麼很丟人的舉動麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦 小夜一直都很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大男人很難在別人面前吃甜食的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人就不行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是唯芳先生想在小夜面前耍帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親不用耍也很帥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會這麼告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 就算他想耍帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜歡甜食的事已經暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神奇名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙甜味 輕飄飄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到「Guimauve」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像碰到某種東西的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與什麼東西的觸感很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是因為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是被丟掉的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過它獨自在那兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說還是流浪狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 要說是流浪狗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得它太淡定穩重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大狗狗麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗崽?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說的話 比狗崽起來還要小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點怪怪的花紋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你叫我名字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該叫過你鞆總班長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸樹大暴投
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}暴投：棒球術語。投手擲出捕手無法接住的球。喻指小夜對逸樹說的話故意裝傻。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜應對得從容淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應對得自如 反而令我鬥志高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是班長哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩點進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這種沒誠意的忽悠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是更衣你自己做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 是別人給做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文人先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「Cafe Guimauve」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上唯一的咖啡店嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶啊喝咖啡之類的店也就那麼一家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那裡的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人為什麼會幫更衣做便當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像他是父親高中時候的學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似他和你爸爸年歲差很多吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不是同時期在學校裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 逸樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有希望啊 逸樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道「Guimauve」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是點心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是那個跟棉花糖很像的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那觸感似乎跟什麼很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒吃過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「啾」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像「啾」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啾～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是對「啾」沒反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小逸樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會更努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不趕緊吃 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若谷伊斯商店的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吧 那個店的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鎮上唯一的麵包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃的話 除了哭沒有別的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上全是唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連超市也只有一家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不是唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是小鎮 感覺倒更像是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人太少了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過疏地區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 是個寧靜的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學喜歡這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 時真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 還沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不趕快吃 午飯時間就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂　肚子不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空著肚子會變得悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要向我道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且讚賞了文人先生的便當 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路殺出個程咬金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易一起吃飯增進了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不要留下傷疤就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要發呆到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣好晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空赤霞飄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如父親 說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣服 也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如父親 說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:16:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快活很好 但那首歌就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來庫房有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要找的東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是何人為「古物」命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然無論在哪本書中都沒有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正如其名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實自古便是噬人之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噬人之物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與它對戰過的小夜應該最清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 唯一能打倒它們的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親也曾手持御神刀與「古物」戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果被擊敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護父親　還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我結果還是遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看電視看得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞還是喜劇?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視購物還是記錄片?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜藝節目還是音樂節目?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.84,0:23:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行節目還是烹飪節目?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那些…倒底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣家的秘密終於要被揭開了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那驚人的真相是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人心莫測